title: Lipstick, red heels and purse only clues in TV Star Jodi Huisentruit disappearance
itunes:title: Lipstick, red heels and purse only clues in TV Star Jodi Huisentruit disappearance
description:
When Iowa TV news anchor Jodi Huisentruit failed to show up for her morning show, coworkers knew something was wrong. The popular TV personality is still missing more than two decades later. Nancy Grace reopens the case in a discussion with forensics expert Joseph Scott Morgan -- Author of "Blood Beneath My Feet," forensic psychiatrist Dr. Daniel Bober, and North Carolina family and divorce lawyer Kathleen Murphy.
